en.net/H%E1%BB%93-Ch%C3%AD-Minh/Thanh-minh/poem-zmekfTCVW7OWfbQJqNFJ9Q">Thanh minh - 清明</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/H%E1%BB%93-Ch%C3%AD-Minh/author-a7YEflJr1_rcFKC9dgECgQ">Hồ Chí Minh</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Khu%E1%BA%A5t-Nguy%C3%AAn/Thi%C3%AAn-v%E1%BA%A5n/poem-xfUL0RFU1M6WV9XOi__Sxg">Thiên vấn - 天問</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Khu%E1%BA%A5t-Nguy%C3%AAn/author-2RPFDWkSQLaYkT3rYIGIrQ">Khuất Nguyên</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-Khi%C3%AAm/T%E1%BB%91ng-th%C6%B0%E1%BB%A3ng-th%C6%B0-S%C3%A0i-Trang-Khanh-t%E1%BB%B1/poem-zD7mrwO-43MIHObHTaGOMw">Tống thượng thư Sài Trang Khanh tự - 送尚書柴莊卿序</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-Khi%C3%AAm/author-1_5YGABQESnAmYdOvhbEZQ">Lý Khiêm</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Th%E1%BB%B1c-Hi%E1%BB%81n/V%C3%B4-%C4%91%E1%BB%81-II/poem-Vy-DL7d5-Nm_0zC_flypBg">Vô đề (II) - 無題</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Th%E1%BB%B1c-Hi%E1%BB%81n/author-VNhahLxtqyIrLeDASL0s9Q">Thực Hiền</a>)<br></div>	</div>
